00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:13,880
 over the years, the centuries, right, that really have transformed and revolutionized

3
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:18,800
 how we do things, even the simple things, you know, like a light bulb.

4
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:22,680
 Could you imagine if we didn't have a light bulb?

5
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,680
 Electricity.

6
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,440
 Even an umbrella.

7
